# This will be interpreted by a Python script that will then send the serial
#  data to the MidiStomp.  Then the MidiStomp will interpret that serial data
#  to write the information to the EEPROM.
#
# Use hash-tags as comments
# Ignore empty lines
# Name first of struct, use END as terminator

